quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,Yā 'Ayyuhā Al-Ladhīna 'Āmanū 'Idhā Nūdī Lilşşalāati Min Yawmi Al-Jumu`ati Fās`aw 'Ilá Dhikri Allāhi Wa Dharū Al-Bay`a Dhālikum Khayrun Lakum 'In Kuntum Ta`lamūna
  62,10,Fa'idhā Quđiyati Aş-Şalāatu Fāntashirū Fī Al-'Arđi Wa Abtaghū Min Fađli Allāhi Wa Adhkurū Allāha Kathīrāan La`allakum Tufliĥūna
  62,11,Wa 'Idhā Ra'aw Tijāratan 'Aw Lahwan Anfađđū 'Ilayhā Wa Tarakūka Qā'imāan Qul Mā `Inda Allāhi Khayrun Mina Al-Lahwi Wa Mina At-Tijārati Wa Allāhu Khayru Ar-Rāziqīna